data.description: Welcome to 153 Lake Ridge Drive! This gorgeous 5-bedroom, 3.5 bathroom, two story home is in the ideal neighborhood of Columbia Lakes, and in the Mason school district. As you enter through the front door you are greeted with a light and bright living room and an open concept first floor. Through the living room is the kitchen and dining room! The kitchen features plenty of cabinets and counterspace, granite countertops, an island with an eat-at bar, ceramic tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and newly installed hardwood floors. The dining room features a door that opens to the raised back deck and large backyard, perfect for entertaining guests. Rounding out the remainder of this floor includes an updated half bathroom, an office or playroom with French doors, and access to the attached 2.5 car garage. Upstairs you will find a large loft space, three bedrooms with oversized closets, a large full bathroom, the laundry room, and the expansive primary suite with a walk-in closet and dual sink vanity. The finished lower level has a large rec room with plenty of egress windows, plumbing that is waiting for your future wet bar, a fifth bedroom, full bathroom, and storage space. Additionally, the Mason school district sports program is highly regarded. Both the Varsity Football team and Varsity Soccer team made it to the State Championships! Congrats Bulldogs! This neighborhood is one to be admired with all the amenities it offers: lake access, playground, streetlights, common areas and more! This truly is a must see home! Call today to schedule your private showing!
